  <generalInformation><![CDATA[<p>Spanning 400 kilometres, you won't get bored on a snow sports trip in the Milky Way. All six resorts are different sizes placed at varying altitudes, and each village has a different vibe, so there is something for everyone no matter your age or ability - and what's better is you can even ski two countries in a single day!  </p>]]></generalInformation>
