  <listingDescription><![CDATA[<p>The Milky Way is an international ski area linking Montgenèvre in France with <a data-udi="umb://document/50e23ca4eed84c0d9e0681e29aebcaea" href="/{localLink:umb://document/50e23ca4eed84c0d9e0681e29aebcaea}" title="Sestriere">Sestriere</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/a0b1d3c577424320a9af2e1af08b6887" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a0b1d3c577424320a9af2e1af08b6887}" title="Sauze d'Oulx">Sauze d'Oulx</a>, Sansicario, Cesana and <a data-udi="umb://document/0ef50b40433049599442f2b4e3eb2671" href="/{localLink:umb://document/0ef50b40433049599442f2b4e3eb2671}" title="Claviere" data-anchor="#">Claviere</a> in Italy. Hosting the 2006 Winter Olympics here meant that the ski area was meticulously upgraded.</p>]]></listingDescription>
